    "description": "Joshin Corporation operates an electrical appliance retail and ancillary business in Japan. It offers home appliances, information and communication equipment, entertainment products, housing equipment, and related products, as well as incidental businesses. The company also engages in general renovations, planning, design, and construction of extensions and remodeling, seismic reinforcement; delivery, installation, repair, and maintenance services for home appliances and other related products; and installation and configuration of information equipment and communication equipment. In addition, it provides non-life insurance and life insurance agency services, reinsurance underwriting for non-life insurance, and contracting and management services, as well as operates a store that rents music and video software, used books, etc. The company was formerly known as Joshin Denki Co., Ltd. and changed its name to Joshin Corporation in April 2026. Joshin Corporation was founded in 1948 and is headquartered in Osaka, Japan."
